title: season rewards and alpha client icon
body: I didnt receive season rewards yet or alpha client icon , what is going on riot ?

replies.body:
We were having some issues with getting ranked rewards out to some players, so if you reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), we'll help you out.

The Open Beta has already rolled out to EUNE, so you should see a prompt for it when you Launch the legacy client. Let me know if you have any questions.
